{"tid":2293272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽]請黑警唔好講咩人權起底個d垃圾理由, 6月9同612開始你地已經收埋號碼牌同委任證, 射盲教師個日已經收埋","createTime":"2020-11-20T06:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T02:36:10.000Z","uid":179775,"like":70,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e45c4f4d8a8fa10e8bb47d0a07e4f3450f05e68d","tid":2293272,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:30:22.000Z","msg":"其實都係想集體違規<br />\n想人投訴唔到姐<br />\n<br />\n有無需要通知律師<br />\n如果黑警想用起底作抗辯<br />\n拎612已經收埋可唔可以篤穿佢地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/340926/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%AD%A6%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85%E7%84%A1%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E8%80%85%E5%86%92%E8%AD%A6-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%9F%B7%E5%8B%A4%E7%84%A1%E6%88%B4%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F340926%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BE%2584%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2586%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%259F%25B7%25E5%258B%25A4%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2588%25B4%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%25AD%2589&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=eb8c576c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/340926/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%AD%A6%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85%E7%84%A1%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E8%80%85%E5%86%92%E8%AD%A6-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%9F%B7%E5%8B%A4%E7%84%A1%E6%88%B4%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89</a>"},{"pid":"009cec4d7c2fac723dfda17f1e3e11ced14e055e","tid":2293272,"uid":298757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" cl